                  Our commitment is to help you manage and optimize your spend,
                  effortlessly, and with complete transparency. From simple
                  expense tracking to detailed analytics, you now have the power
                  to understand and control your spending like never before.
                </p>

                <div class='x-between'>
                  <div class='otp box' style='color: black'>{{otp}}</div>
                </div>

                <div class='box' style='color: black'>{{reason}}</div>

                <p>
